PrecisORDER (a) GIVING NOTICE OF DECISIONS NOT TO ADD certain populations of Atlantic Cod and Coho Salmon to the List of Wildlife Species at Risk and to REFER THE ASSESSMENTS done on other aquatic species back to COSEWIC for further information and consideration; and (b) APPROVING THE STATEMENTS to be placed in the Public Registry setting out the reasons for the preceding decisions.
